= merb_mart

merb_mart is an open-source e-commerce engine based on the Merb MVC framework.

Current Dependencies:
 * merb 0.9.1 or above
    * merb-core
    * merb-more
    * merb-plugins
        * merb_datamapper
        * merb_helpers
        * merb_rspec
    * datamapper: currently requires last SVN version of 0.3.0.
                  latest git version seems to be broken with merb_datamapper
                  

merb_mart is a loose port of the Substruct RoR e-commerce application.
http://code.google.com/p/substruct/
http://substruct.subimage.com/